	<title>The amendment to Regulation 8 of the Medical Schemes Act, what does it mean? — Helen Suzman Foundation</title><meta name="twitter:title" content="The amendment to Regulation 8 of the Medical Schemes Act, what does it mean?" /><meta property="og:site_name" content="Helen Suzman Foundation" /><meta property="og:title" content="The amendment to Regulation 8 of the Medical Schemes Act, what does it mean?" /><meta property="og:type" content="website" /><meta name="twitter:site" content="@HelenSuzmanFdn" /><meta property="og:article:publisher" content="https://www.facebook.com/helensuzmanfoundation" /><meta name="twitter:description" content="This Brief discusses the amendment to Regulation 8 of the Medical Schemes Act and what it actually means to members of medical schemes and other stakeholders." /><meta name="twitter:url" content="https://hsf.org.za/publications/hsf-briefs/the-amendment-to-regulation-of-the-medical-schemes-act" /><meta property="og:description" content="This Brief discusses the amendment to Regulation 8 of the Medical Schemes Act and what it actually means to members of medical schemes and other stakeholders." /><meta property="og:url" content="https://hsf.org.za/publications/hsf-briefs/the-amendment-to-regulation-of-the-medical-schemes-act" /><meta name="twitter:image" content="https://hsf.org.za/@@site-logo/HSF_Full_Logo_Black_Long.png" /><meta property="og:image" content="https://hsf.org.za/@@site-logo/HSF_Full_Logo_Black_Long.png" /><meta property="og:image:type" content="image/png" /><meta name="description" content="This Brief discusses the amendment to Regulation 8 of the Medical Schemes Act and what it actually means to members of medical schemes and other stakeholders." /><meta name="DC.description" content="This Brief discusses the amendment to Regulation 8 of the Medical Schemes Act and what it actually means to members of medical schemes and other stakeholders." /><meta name="keywords" content="Briefs, Health" /><meta name="DC.subj